==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tetanize
<hw>Tet"a*nize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <fld>(Physiol.)</fld>
<def>To throw, as a muscle, into a state of permanent contraction; to
cause tetanus in. See <er>Tetanus</er>, <pos>n.</pos>, 2.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tetanoid</ent>⟦br⟧
